# Copy to .dev.vars and fill in. .dev.vars is gitignored — never commit secrets.
#
# Most non-secret values for local dev already live in wrangler.jsonc › top-level
# vars (LOG_LEVEL, ALLOWED_ORIGINS, FEVRIPS_UPSTREAM_BASE_URL). This file only
# carries secrets and tenant-flavored overrides.

# Optional: override the upstream FEV RIPS base URL. Defaults to the staging
# upstream so local dev never accidentally writes to production.
# FEVRIPS_UPSTREAM_BASE_URL=https://rips-stage.matrixmdsoftware.com
